Fix committed in revision 1388517. Please test.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13460901" author="fhess" created="Fri, 21 Sep 2012 22:41:05 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks, seems to be fixed testing with revision 1388555.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
